        <hr>
        
      Being from Central Africa
      <br />
      <em> Democratic of the Congo</em>

      <br />
      <img
        src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/shecodesio-production/uploads/files/000/059/716/original/Flag_of_the_Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo.svg.png?1671499165"
