        <br>
       <div class="Hair">The braided crown that you see Beyonce wearing (middle picture), is native to Mangbetu people of Congo. It is thin braids woven into a crown and is used to appreciate the culture of skull elongation among the tribe.
        The other hairstyle is just a traditional style used heavily in Congo. Whenever you see the hairstyle, you know its from the Congo. </div>
  
